            "id": "fc_house",
            "label": "Housing & Place",
            "color": "#a85830",
            "desc": "Where you live decides most of the rest. Housing in America is the largest household expense, the primary route to family wealth for those who have it, and the locked door for those who don't. Where you live shapes which schools, which jobs, which air, which futures.",
