                "label": "Political Science",
                "color": "#3858a8",
                "desc": "The study of political systems, power, governance, and behavior. Political science asks how power is obtained, how it is exercised, and how it can be constrained. Its findings are often more useful to those seeking power than to those trying to limit it.",
