    "time": "centuries · ten thousand years",
    "desc": "The long record of what humans have tried, built, destroyed, and tried again. History is not a story of progress — it is a story of oscillation. The patterns repeat because the underlying animal changes very slowly. But cultures change fast. And cultures carry the code for empires.",
